Maxima's optics glanced up at the alarm lights. "Blast!" just as the clone 
finished. 

She turned around to face the clone. Motioning the clone forward. As it 
stepped forward she motioned to another area. "There. Stay in the chamber until I 
return." 

The clone obeyed & hid in the chamber as Maxima raced out of the room. 
Charging down the corridor, she glanced into the command room. Hydras was gone. 
"Bloody hell," somehow she didn't like this. 

As she ran back down the corridor, she punched a panel as a weapons cache 
showed itself. Grabbing 2 major damage weapons. Then took off. 

Racing down to the exit where she saw Perceptor & the tail end of Blackstorm. 
Whipping out. "Perceptor! Report!" was all she knew. Wanting to know what was 
going on. 

--part1_a.32a1172e.2c32350c_boundary
